He refused to cooperate with the IMF, harassed the private sector, and cleaned up the National Institute of Statistics and Census INDEC, which subsequently fined the official inflation statistics.
Can Fern<0xC3><0xA1>ndez now take a more moderate path?
It called on the private sector and trade union leaders to talk.
And according to official statements, wage increases will be limited to 18% next year.
